<p itemprop="description">A senior data scientist designs and leads data science projects, providing guidance to others and taking ownership of complex analytical challenges.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Design and lead the implementation of data science projects</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Work collaboratively with a range of experts in support of organisational objectives</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Communicate effectively and challenge delivery plans and priorities</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Provide guidance and mentoring to junior data scientists</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Understand and apply data ethics principles in data science work</li>
    </ul>
</section>

